social_posts.post_text: What an amazing time celebrating your birthday with you on the West Coast. Wishing you an abundance of love, laughter, joy and prosperity now and forever. I love you 💕
I Pray everyone started this year with an “All Things New” mindset. Sending you all love!
Empowering each other everyday! Happy International Women’s Day!
Breathe and have Faith… 💜

I love my family
Shout out to my beautiful girl on all her success💕💕💕
Join us May 12th for the Caribbean Masters Reception! Portion of the proceeds will be donated to @carolmarajfoundation to help woman across the world! See you there!

“She is clothed with strength and dignity, and she laughs without fear of the future. When she speaks, her words are wise, and she gives instructions with kindness. She carefully watches everything in her household and suffers nothing from laziness. Her children stand and bless her. Her husband praises her: “There are many virtuous and capable women in the world, but you surpass them all!””
Proverbs 31:25-29

@carolinamusicvideoawards and @blockloveclt is so excited to announce that the very beautiful and amazing @theofficialcarolmaraj will be coming to Charlotte, North Carolina for the 7th Annual Carolina Music Video Awards on August 5th Luxe Event Venue. We will be inducting @theofficialcarolmaraj into the Hall of Fame. She is a gospel singer, songwriter and a domestic violence advocate. We are so honored to present her with this luxurious award and we can’t wait to do so. This event is hosted by: @power98fm @vonyettaisnow and @1025theblock @jervayv Music by: @djsns This award is sponsored by: @topshelfent864 @5ewup Thank you’s to: @alicia_world @itsambassadorsarita This event is going to be the talk of the town. 🌟 We’re excited to extend a warm invitation to our upcoming lunch and launch event dedicated to fostering women’s empowerment and mental health awareness! 🌟

At the She Can Foundation, we believe in creating an inclusive ecosystem where women not only survive but flourish both professionally and personally. 🌷 Our commitment to empowerment aligns perfectly with our mission, and we’re thrilled to invite you to be a part of this transformative experience.

📅 January 14th, 2024 ⏰ 12-5pm 📍Charlotte Motor Speedway Ballroom

✨ What to Expect:

Engaging discussions on women’s empowerment
Insights into mental health awareness
Networking opportunities with like-minded individuals
Delicious lunch to nourish both body and soul
Let’s come together to celebrate the strength, resilience, and achievements of women while raising awareness about mental health challenges. Your presence will contribute to building a community where every woman can thrive.

Spread the word and bring your friends, colleagues, and loved ones. Together, let’s make a positive impact and create a ripple effect of empowerment and support.

www.theshecanfoundation.com for Tickets!

#EmpowerWomen #MentalHealthMatters #InclusionForAll #FlourishTogether

See you there!
